data.enText: the art or activity of preparing and cooking food

tr: the act of preparing something (as food) by the application of heat
example: cooking can be a great art
people are needed who have experience in cookery
he left the preparation of meals to his wife

value.def: Cookery is the activity of preparing and cooking food.

example.ex: The school runs cookery courses throughout the year.
example.tran: 这个学校常年开设烹饪学习班。
